From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: X6873 TWRP <twrp@infinix.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2025 09:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Change haptics activation file path for Infinix X6873

Infinix X6873 uses a different path for haptics activation.
Change from standard path to device-specific path.

diff --git a/events.cpp b/events.cpp
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/events.cpp
+++ b/events.cpp
@@ -55,7 +55,7 @@
 #define VIBRATOR_PATH "/sys/class/timed_output/vibrator/enable"
 #endif

-#ifndef VIBRATOR_PATH
+#ifndef VIBRATOR_CUSTOM_PATH
 #define VIBRATOR_PATH "/sys/class/leds/vibrator/activate"
 #endif

